OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,F"This country belongs to you as much
OL,7,Fas any of us": The Jewish community
OL,8,Fhas been told in an open letter signed
OL,9,Fby religious leaders and leading
OL,10,Ffigures from across British society.
OL,12,FThe letter, co-ordinated by the
OL,13,FTogether Coalition says antisemitism
OL,14,Fis "a problem for all of us to fix"
OL,15,Ffollowing a wave of attacks on Jews in
OL,16,Fthe UK in recent weeks, including the
OL,17,Fstabbing of two men in Golders Green,
OL,18,Fnorth London.
OL,26,@vD@DOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778371373
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,F"The spectre of Jewish people being
OL,7,Fstabbed at random in the street,
OL,8,Fkilled defending their synagogues and
OL,9,FJewish infrastructure being firebombed
OL,10,Ffeel like a nightmare from another
OL,11,Ftime," the letter says.
OL,13,F"A throwback to grainy images of
OL,14,Fsomewhere else, not delivered in
OL,15,Ftechnicolour from the streets of
OL,16,FLondon in 2026.
OL,18,F"This is not a problem for Jewish
OL,19,Fpeople to have to respond to. This is
OL,20,Fa problem for all of us to fix."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@FO]uD@AOUzD@AOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778371373
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,FThe letter, which as well as religious
OL,7,Fleaders has been signed by leading
OL,8,Ffigures from business, sport and
OL,9,Fmedia, comes ahead of a rally in
OL,10,Fsupport of Britain's Jewish community
OL,11,Foutside Downing Street on Sunday.
OL,13,F"As leaders of British organisations `
OL,14,Fwith different views on faith,
OL,15,Fpolitics, foreign policy and pretty
OL,16,Fmuch everything else ` we come
OL,17,Ftogether today to send a message to
OL,18,Four Jewish brothers and sisters," the
OL,19,Fletter says.
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
