OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778371373
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,F"This country belongs to you as much
OL,7,Fas any of us.
OL,9,F"Along with the vast majority of
OL,10,FBritish people we share a vision of
OL,11,Four country where people of different
OL,12,Ffaiths, races and beliefs come
OL,13,Ftogether to build communities and a
OL,14,Fcountry that we can all be proud of."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
