OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,FSignatories of the letter include the
OL,7,FFootball Association, the Premier
OL,8,FLeague, faith leaders from the Church
OL,9,Fof England, Muslim, Hindu, Sikh and
OL,10,FZoroastrian communities, the National
OL,11,FLottery Community Fund, the Women's
OL,12,FInstitute and many more across media,
OL,13,Fsport and charities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
