CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778371373
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,FBrendan Cox, co-founder of the
OL,7,FTogether Coalition, said: "This is an
OL,8,Fincredibly powerful statement of
OL,9,Fsolidarity with the British Jewish
OL,10,Fcommunity from every section of our
OL,11,Fsociety. But it's more than that, it's
OL,12,Fa commitment to action to fight
OL,13,Fantisemitism together. That's what we
OL,14,Furgently need.
OL,16,F"Too often antisemitism is seen as a
OL,17,Fproblem just for the Jewish community.
OL,18,FIt's not. It's a cancer in our society
OL,19,Fthat undermines the kind of inclusive
OL,20,Fcountry that we all want to build.
OL,26,@oD@[OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778371373
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,F"Extremists are trying to divide us,
OL,7,Fto target minorities on the basis of
OL,8,Ftheir race or religion and to turn
OL,9,Fcommunity against community. We won't
OL,10,Flet them."
OL,12,FJulie Siddiqi, co-chair of the UK
OL,13,FMuslim Network and one of the
OL,14,Fsignatories, said: "Antisemitism is
OL,15,Freal, it's growing and it's totally
OL,16,Funacceptable. We have a duty not just
OL,17,Fto condemn it ` but to take it on
OL,18,Fwherever we find it, including in our
OL,19,Fown communities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]vD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
