SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778371373
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,F"As British Muslims we know what it's
OL,7,Flike to face hatred and violence
OL,8,Fbecause of our faith ` that shared
OL,9,Fexperience should make British Jews
OL,10,Fand British Muslims allies in tackling
OL,11,Fextremism."
OL,13,FOrganisers of the protest against
OL,14,Fantisemitism outside Downing Street on
OL,15,FSunday expect thousands of people to
OL,16,Fattend.
OL,18,FSpeakers, including the chief rabbi,
OL,19,Fwill feature at the rally organised by
OL,20,Fthe Jewish Leadership Council and the
OL,21,FBoard of Deputies of British Jews.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
