OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778371373
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,FChief Rabbi Sir Ephraim Mirvis said:
OL,7,F"This letter is a powerful riposte to
OL,8,Fthe hateful extremists who have
OL,9,Ftargeted the Jewish community in
OL,10,Frecent weeks.
OL,12,F"It is heartening to see some of
OL,13,FBritain's best-known institutions from
OL,14,Fthe world of business, sport, faith
OL,15,Fand civil society standing together
OL,16,Fagainst anti-Jewish hatred.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
