SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778371373
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,F"My hope is that where these
OL,7,Finstitutions have led, others will
OL,8,Ffollow, in workplaces, boardrooms,
OL,9,Fclassrooms and on social media, so
OL,10,Fthat we can finally begin to tackle
OL,11,Fthis scourge together."
