OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,FOrganisers of the rally, which starts
OL,7,Fat 1pm on Sunday, have called on the
OL,8,FBritish public to "face down
OL,9,Fextremists" following multiple alleged
OL,10,Fantisemitic attacks in recent months.
OL,12,FKeith Black, chairman of the Jewish
OL,13,FLeadership Council, said: "For two and
OL,14,Fa half years we have warned about the
OL,15,Fstaggering rise in antisemitism in
OL,16,Fthis country. Yet, antisemitism in
OL,17,FBritain is not just rising, it is
OL,18,Fescalating into deadly acts of
OL,19,Fviolence and terror.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@KO]uD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778371373
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'a problem for all of
OL,4,Cus to fix', religious leaders say
OL,6,F"This Sunday at 1pm, people will
OL,7,Fgather outside Downing Street to stand
OL,8,Fagainst this hatred and face down
OL,9,Fextremists. It should not just be Jews
OL,10,Fwho turn up. British values are being
OL,11,Fchallenged by antisemites, and we have
OL,12,Fto stand against it together."
OL,14,FThe Metropolitan Police announced this
OL,15,Fweek a community protection team of
OL,16,F100 extra officers to help safeguard
OL,17,Fthe Jewish community, despite Sir Mark
OL,18,FRowley's previous call for 300 extra
OL,19,Fpolice officers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
